title: #151:  The Lost Years Of Jesus Christ with Shaan Joshi
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome return champion, comedian Shaan Joshi to the show to discuss the unknown years of the life of Jesus Christ and the place Jesus he went and the people he met. Spoiler alert: Japan Jesus is my favorite by the way.
Please check out my new special Armogeddon and Zero Fucks on Vimeo!
